    "Similarly, we fine-tuned the versions of MLP-Mixer: Mixer-B/16 and Mixer-L/16, with the provided pre-trained weights, where they were followed (11) by the same architecture as ViT's base model.",
    "We used a BCE loss function, and the Adam optimizer with an initial learning rate of 1e -4, β1 = 0.9, β2 = 0.999 and epsilon equal to 1e -7.",
